title: 855. Top 10 Players in Bills vs Rams Season Opener & Impactful Rookies
itunes:title: 855. Top 10 Players in Bills vs Rams Season Opener & Impactful Rookies
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys recap Week 1 of college football with a focus on the classic North Carolina vs App State game, Georgia dominating Oregon, and much more. Next, the pair draft their top 10 players from the Bills vs Rams season opener. To wrap up the show, the duo break down Bucky's list of the most impactful rookies in each division, while doing a deep dive on one per conference.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
